end

function reset(_obj,player)
    timerParams={}
    timerParams.identifier='screenSpawnTimer'
    timerParams.function_name='timerTick'
    timerParams.parameters = {self.getPosition(),self.getRotation()}
    timerParams.function_owner=self
    timerParams.delay = 0.01
    timerParams.repetitions = 1

    Timer.create(timerParams)
    copy({_obj})
    self.destruct()
end

function timerTick(_param)
    newObj=paste({_obj})
    newObj[1].setPosition(_param[1])
    newObj[1].setRotation(_param[2])
end
